info.author: Yong Shean
info.description:
This tool demonstrates the object recognition using OverFeat by Yann Lecun group.

OverFeat is a Convolutional Network-based image features extractor and classifier. More details of implementation on http://cilvr.nyu.edu/doku.php?id=software:overfeat:start. The underlying system is described in http://arxiv.org/abs/1312.6229.
info.name: overfeat_gui
info.summary: A simple program that captures webcam image and recognise the objects in it.
